text.section: Any person who violates the provisions of subsection (2) of KRS 376.050 shall be guilty of a Class D felony.
Any person who violates any of the provisions of KRS 376.060 or 376.070 shall be guilty of a Class A misdemeanor.

law.history: Amended 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 463, sec. 43, effective July 14, 1992. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 2467, 2467a-2, 2467b-4.
